  "elapsed_s": 90.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And perhaps some of them were deprived of food for weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who knows how many of them died in travelling there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember seeing them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my mother used to bring them-- bring me with her when she was preparing some kind of food for some of these people with other women of the shelter there, other Jewish women, that they, between them, they were saving from their meager foods in order to give to these people there that were dying of food-- very weak, very [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] desperately-looking people.",
      "word_count": 71
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- this what stick of my mind in the, the time as it was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In one of these gatherings, I was ask to play, to bring my musical instruments and perform.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For this--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I never will forget this amazing impression that I saw in the faces of this people when I was performing, specially after the time I was finishing my songs, to perform for them.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Obviously, my performance was touching very deep portions of their hearts, these deep strings there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I was seeing tears in their eyes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
